<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>ReservasBot — Login</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background: #0f0f13; display: flex; min-height: 100vh; }
    .left { flex: 1; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 50%, #0f3460 100%); display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; padding: 60px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
    .left::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: -50%; left: -50%; width: 200%; height: 200%; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(124,111,255,0.1) 0%, transparent 60%); }
    .left h1 { font-size: 42px; color: white; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px; position: relative; }
    .left h1 span { color: #7C6FFF; }
    .left p { font-size: 18px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); max-width: 400px; line-height: 1.6; position: relative; }
    .features { margin-top: 48px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; position: relative; }
    .feature { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; }
    .feature-icon { width: 40px; height: 40px; background: rgba(124,111,255,0.2); border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 18px; }
    .feature-text { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); font-size: 15px; }
    .right { width: 480px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 40px; }
    .card { width: 100%; max-width: 400px; }
    .card-header { margin-bottom: 36px; }
    .card-header h2 { font-size: 28px; color: #e2e2e2; font-weight: 600; }
    .card-header p { color: #666; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 6px; }
    .campo { margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .campo label { display: block; font-size: 12px; color: #888; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .campo input { width: 100%; padding: 12px 16px; background: #17171f; border: 1px solid #2a2a35; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 14px; color: #e2e2e2; outline: none; transition: border .2s; }
    .campo input:focus { border-color: #7C6FFF; }
    .btn { width: 100%; padding: 13px; background: #7C6FFF; color: white; border: none; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 15px; cursor: pointer; font-weight: 500; transition: background .2s; margin-top: 8px; }
    .btn:hover { background: #6a5ce8; }
    .error { background: rgba(220,38,38,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(220,38,38,0.3); color: #ff6b6b; padding: 12px 16px; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .link { text-align: center; margin-top: 24px; font-size: 14px; color: #666; }
    .link a { color: #7C6FFF; text-decoration: none; }
    .link a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    @media (max-width: 768px) { .left { display: none; } .right { width: 100%; } }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="left">
    <h1>Reservas<span>Bot</span></h1>
    <p>El asistente inteligente que gestiona las reservas de tu restaurante 24/7</p>
    <div class="features">
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">📞</div>
        <div class="feature-text">Atiende llamadas automáticamente con IA</div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">💬</div>
        <div class="feature-text">Gestiona reservas por WhatsApp</div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">📊</div>
        <div class="feature-text">Panel de control en tiempo real</div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">✉️</div>
        <div class="feature-text">Notificaciones y recordatorios automáticos</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="right">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <h2>Bienvenido</h2>
        <p>Inicia sesión en tu panel de reservas</p>
      </div>
      <% if (error) { %>
        <div class="error"><%= error %></div>
      <% } %>
      <form method="POST" action="/login">
        <div class="campo">
          <label>Email</label>
          <input type="email" name="email" required placeholder="tu@email.com" autofocus>
        </div>
        <div class="campo">
          <label>Contraseña</label>
          <input type="password" name="password" required placeholder="••••••••">
        </div>
        <button class="btn" type="submit">Entrar →</button>
      </form>
      <div class="link">¿No tienes cuenta? <a href="/registro">Regístrate gratis</a></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>